latestIgtvVideos.title: “Model”
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Yes you know the word “model” & you might define it as person who promote or display brand products.
Things which you need to know is something that might tease your mind if it’s stereotyped.
A model is not a prop only to carry outfits but to live in it.
A model makes outfits alive even if it’s a project with nudity that doesn’t mean it’s a “yes” to every dirty mindset or nude desires but to make photographer’s frame look aesthetically productive.
Hence, from now onwards before you talk about models you should know that a model is someone who brings the trend in you , introduce you to lifestyle full of new fashion.
And one should think twice before judging a model’s look, outfits ,professional appearance with his/her personal life. — DO SHARE IF YOU LIKE IT, WE CAN TOGETHER MAKE A CHANGE —

latestPosts.caption:
THE YELLOW BLAZER 

Introducing our Glamorous Yellow Blazer, a symbol of sophistication and style. Crafted in exquisite embroidered fabric, it exudes elegance and flair. The corporate-inspired design, coupled with full sleeves, adds a touch of professionalism to your ensemble. This blazer is a versatile addition to your wardrobe, perfect for both formal events and adding a chic edge to casual looks. The vibrant yellow hue adds a pop of color, making it a statement piece. Elevate your fashion game with this blend of timeless elegance and contemporary style. Step out confidently, exuding charm and confidence in this stunning yellow blazer.
